{
  "stem": "2522.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We really were being continually marginalized to higher, higher up, to recede further and further into the mountains where, where-- you know, there were no helicopters, no paratroops in those days.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we just withdrew further and further away from where we were reached because the lower ranges of the countryside after November 15 were, were totally occupied.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was much treason going on and police informing of partisans who, who were captured that way.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, all the time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we, we had-- you know, we cut down-- I, I don't think-- after October 28, I think we only did two raids.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After that, it was just sheer survival.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Particularly after December, it was just sheer survival.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a mountain on which we were called [NON-ENGLISH] which is-- which is-- you know, you can barely survive there if you are well fed and well clothed, but we were on that mountain.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's where I'm going to be next, yeah, Sunday night, a week from this coming Sunday.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the clothing was terrible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For instance, my shoes were pitiful.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And no socks, so you wrapped your feet in, in, in just, like, bandages.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I still have frostbite.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, well, you know, damage by frostbite.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and you got very easily infected.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see, there was no sulfa drugs, no nothing, so, so by and large when you rubbed your skin-- most of the time you were wet, and you did not have proper clothing or proper shoes.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If your feet go rubbed, the skin got-- you know, gets soft and, you know, you could almost peel it off.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that got infected, so there was just lots of infection.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
